{"tid":1535041,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動及公海】9月8日 美領撐法案祈禱集會","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:01:33.000Z","uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"99c38930c91ffbc526e2acdb96ae74412c5f752e","tid":1535041,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:08:10.000Z","msg":"[center]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGsKsXy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGsKsXy.gif&h=2996ed29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTp1AJS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTp1AJS.png&h=24c3c0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnxyoC2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnxyoC2.gif&h=9a775d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9月8日撐法案萬人祈禱集會</span></span><br />\n地點：遮打花園 美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n時間：9月8日 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">12:30</span></strong> (遮打)  <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">14:00</span></strong> (美領)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">宗教集會，不需申請不反對通知書，自行評估風險<br />\n(因鄰近禮賓府，很大機會不獲批，反而不合法)</span>"},{"pid":"588a04c1a7e44284cf2ed65487b38fc1dcbe4789","tid":1535041,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a49c15d426f52d06fd6362a4fbc8d28149aec69c","tid":1535041,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83c421e7b08b55a41b0795dbaefcc2e63cc2f9c5","tid":1535041,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">行動：</span><br />\n由教徒帶領為香港人權及民主祈禱<br />\n提交巨式請願信，並供在場人士簽署<br />\n喊叫英文號，包括撐法案訴求<br />\n&quot;Free Hong Kong, Pass the act.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">活動為和理非，不容許有任何衝擊行為</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">時間表：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skc24zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkc24zk.png&h=3cadacbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2xyrND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2xyrND.png&h=1b101412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>12：30 </strong>遮打花園祈禱集會，評估人數<br />\n<strong>13：30 </strong>不經禮賓府，沿金鍾道紅棉路方向前往美領<br />\n<strong>13：50</strong> 經過花園道聖若瑟堂，唱聖歌及祈禱<br />\n<strong>14：00 </strong>美國領事館祈禱集會 <br />\n(如人數太多，以流水式在美領對出繞圈集會)<br />\n<strong>15：30  </strong>提交巨式請願信 / 請願信<br />\n<strong>17：00  </strong>離開禮賓府及美領相關範圍 (<span style=\"color: red;\">和平散去</span>)"},{"pid":"8821824e4b0b621cdfb44fb491231d148512f6a2","tid":1535041,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">行動：</span><br />\n由教徒帶領為香港人權及民主祈禱<br />\n提交巨式請願信，並供在場人士簽署<br />\n喊叫英文號，包括撐法案訴求<br />\n&quot;Free Hong Kong, Pass the act.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">活動為和理非，不容許有任何衝擊行為</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">時間表：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skc24zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkc24zk.png&h=3cadacbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2xyrND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2xyrND.png&h=1b101412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12：30 遮打花園祈禱集會，評估人數<br />\n13：30 不經禮賓府，沿金鍾道紅棉路方向前往美領<br />\n13：50 經過花園道聖若瑟堂，唱聖歌及祈禱<br />\n14：00 美國領事館祈禱集會 <br />\n(如人數太多，以流水式在美領對出繞圈集會)<br />\n15：30  提交巨式請願信 / 請願信<br />\n17：00  離開禮賓府及美領相關範圍 (<span style=\"color: red;\">和平散去</span>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">目前要做：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n1. 一人一信向美領通知集會+表達訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n電話: (852) 2523-9011<br />\n電子郵件: information_resource_center_hk@yahoo.com<br />\n電子郵件: HKPressTeam@state.gov<br />\n<br />\n範本：<br />\nDear sir or madam,<br />\n<br />\nAccording to the information from the web and social platform, there will be a peaceful assembly outside your office (Consulate General of the US) at Hong Kong time 14:00 on 8th September,2016 (this Sunday) in which a petition for the urge of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act will be expressed and a letter is hoped to be passed to your officer.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, I am writing to hopefully notify you for the event and ask that if there will be special arrangement such as assigning a officer to receive the letter on that day? It would be appreciated.<br />\n<br />\nI am also a supporter of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act. And I hope the voice of the Hong Kong people can be delivered to the US and related department.Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\n(你的名字)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>2. 需要有英文好巴寫請願信</strong></span><br />\n正常SIZE 及 巨型請願信各一封<br />\n巨型請願信內文較簡單，供集會人士簽署<br />\n如冇職員接信，正常SIZE星期一遞交<br />\n巨型請願信則放在美領門口，如圖<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezgfFmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezgfFmt.jpg&h=2f5218bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>3. 打印當日文宣及道具(如美國旗)</strong></span><br />\n建議一人一國旗，下面可打印：<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9UdrvE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9UdrvE.png&h=c7454fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7aj6wD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7aj6wD.png&h=b55903f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrCiDc6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrCiDc6.png&h=68b4225c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOLoPk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOLoPk2.png&h=27b41922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>4. 入TG討論公海</strong></span><br />\n入TG討論詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=432945e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ</a>"},{"pid":"2cf210e6b5a6be1a46788fd005106437c241a584","tid":1535041,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"我要祈禱，祝福香港"},{"pid":"2eee0b76ca0f908f598550e5658fe41eecef9330","tid":1535041,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港 時代革命</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"aaf6a5556c60eba861ad18a823eca70971d9b07e","tid":1535041,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c0a3ba7b4542c50ab2bfc6fbe1ca63c0742a517e","tid":1535041,"uid":108751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b131287b96dd45bb24e9667ec0326984f15f9e6","tid":1535041,"uid":108751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime